<i>Posted by Odicya on 05-21-2003 12:35 AM:</i>

<p><b> Hate Plane and The Calander</b></p>

<p>After review we have decided to remove the Plane of Hate from the calander. However, before the plane was revised several guilds had already previously reserved the Plane of Hate. We have decided to ask the Bert Hall server to acknowledge and honor those reservations until June 15th 2003. Any reservation made after June 15th 2003 will be considered null and void. <br />
<br />
<br />
An announcement is placed at the top/bottom of all Bert Hall forums.<!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE: postbit_signature -->
